{{London Gazette|issue=62666|supp=y|page=B2|date=8 June 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Personal life ==\nHe is married to Samantha, a veterinary surgeon and liveryman of the [[Worshipful Company of Woolmen]]. They have two daughters, Grace and Charlotte.<ref name=mayorbiog/>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-civ}}\n{{s-bef| before = [[Andrew Parmley|Sir Andrew Parmley]]}} \n{{s-ttl|title=[[Lord Mayor of London]]|years=2017\u20132018}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Peter Estlin]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bowman, Charles}}\n[[Category:1961 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People educated at Uppingham School]]\n[[Category:Alumni of the University of Bristol]]\n[[Category:Knights Bachelor]]\n[[Category:British accountants]]\n[[Category:21st-century lord mayors of London]]\n[[Category:21st-century British politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century English politicians]]\n", "name_user": "J947", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eCity of London:clean up,typo(s) fixed: 2015-16 \u2192 2015\u201316", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Bowman_(accountant)"}
